data.description: SELLERS ARE READY TO PASS HOME UNTO NEW FAMILY!!NEW PRICE!! NEW ROOF!!! NEW DECK!! NEW FENCE!!!NEW REFRIGERATOR/FREEZER! This fantastic 3 bedroom 2 bath + bonus room home updated in 2022. Completely remodelded kitchen. Open floor plan , great for entertaining.  New stove, microwave, beautiful countertops, new disposal.  Large laundry room with cabinets, folding area, built in shelving AND space for 2nd refrigerator.  Primary bedroom has custom built closet, full bath with soaking tub,  and French doors that open to new 10 X14  wood deck.   Ceiling fans throughout, 2 driveways for off street parking. Walking distance to Kenner Discovery School, .07 miles from Ochsner Kenner. . This home is eligible for $10,000 assistance,  Call Ariel Waterman 985-674-8267 (First Horizon)
